Invocation Name: motown magic
des: Step into the soulful world of Motown Magic with Brandi Brown, where every beat resonates with the heart and soul of the Motown era. Celebrating the rich legacy of Motown Records, our station brings you timeless hits from legends like Stevie Wonder, Marvin Gaye, and Diana Ross. Whether you're a lifelong fan or new to the magic, tune in and let the unforgettable groove of Motown fill your heart and soul.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
